					<h1>Answering Services &#8211; Why is Answerplus the preferred Answering Service?</h1>					
					<p>Our answering service and <a href="http://www.answerplus.ca/call-centre/">call centre</a> services design team becomes fully versed on each clientâ€™s desired outcome before creating a call processing protocol to meet their individual needs. Then Answerplus provides the great voices and engaging personalities that will express our clientâ€™s corporate goals to their callers.</p>
<h2>Who is Answerplus?</h2>
<p>Answerplus is a 24/7 inbound answering service and call center with locations in Toronto, Hamilton, Calgary, and Montreal, acting as the voice of companies who have made the decision to outsource their incoming contact center, phone, and data communications. Learn more about our <a href="http://www.answerplus.ca/about-us/call_centre_beliefs/">Core Values and Purpose</a> to contribute to our customers&#8217; success and <a href="http://www.answerplus.ca/about-us/call_centre_beliefs/">our beliefs</a> on our about us page, and then read our testimonials to see how we back it up.</p>
<h2>Award Winning Call Center Services</h2>
<p>For 18 consecutive years, Answerplus Call Center has been the recipient of the <a href="http://www.answerplus.ca/outstanding-service-brings-national-award-answer-plus-wins-cam-x-award-of-excellence/">CAM-X Award of Excellence</a>. Earning the prestigious Diamond Award for such enduring excellence within the call centre services industry is no small feat. We have everything you need to help create success in your business.</p>
<h2>Answering Services Available:</h2>
<div style="width: 300px; float: left;">
